Reversed: `[1, 0]` -> wait, least significant first extraction gives `[0, 1]`. Reversed gives `[1, 0]`.
Set continuation bit on all but last: `[1 | 0x80, 0]` -> `[0x81, 0x00]`. Matches example `81 00`.

